and Black wins material.}) 15... Qf5 16. Qd3 Nbd5 17. Bf2 Qg6 18. Rad1 Nh5 {
Black is already slightly better. The game finally ended in a draw, but Black
has no problems at all.} 19. Nc5 Qxd3 20. Nxd3 Rfe8 21. Rfe1 Nhf6 22. a3 Kf8
