{[#] In general, when our opponent has the space advantage, we typically use
two strategies to neutralize it: 1. pawn breaks: to get more space for our
pieces or transform into a more active pawn structure 2. piece exchanges: also
to get more space for our pieces and also to exchange opponent's more active
pieces We will see how to use these strategies as Black in the Slav  Defence.} 
*

