3... Nf6 4. Nc3 dxc4 5. e4 (5. e3 {is considered to be harmless for Black} b5
6. a4 b4 7. Na2 e6 8. Bxc4 Bb7 {[%cal Yb8d7,Yc6c5,Yf8e7] White regains the
