11... e5 $3 12. dxe5 d4 $1 13. exd4 Rb8 14. Qa6 Nxd4 $19 {AND WHITE CAN
RESIGN!!!}) (8. Nf3 Nge7 9. Bb5 O-O 10. O-O Qb6 $132) 8... Bxc3+ $1 (8... Nge7
$4 9. Qxb4 {is something you dont want to do !}) 9. Qxc3 (9. bxc3 Nge7 10.
